snippet.title: Tomb Raider: 10th Anniversary Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Peter Connelly, the composer for Tomb Raider 4-AOD, sent us this previously unseen trailer for the cancelled Tomb Raider: the 10th Anniversary Edition. 
Give Peter's page a like:
https://www.facebook.com/peterconnellymusic/

See more exclusive Tomb Raider: Anniversary Edition content:
https://www.tomb-of-ash.com/tomb-raider-the-10th-anniversary-edition/
